                        <interp inst="t18480612-name-389" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM MILLER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, B</hi> 32.) I took the prisoner. He triedto get away, and beckoned to two other boys to come up to him—there wassome sawdust on his knees, and also on the floor of the counting-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was running to stop the boy, and they caught me.</p>
